author: Hero Hei
description:
The official SAG-AFTRA video game strike seems to be ending but many communities including industry workers say the "damage is already done". The "collective work refusal" against Hoyoverse is not apart of this official strike and the terms of the agreement so we will see if the VA try to continue that attempt.
